about.summary: Execute code when certain modules are imported

name: importhook
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "importhook" %}
{% set version = "1.0.6" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 04b20acaec8330b423762d4f2a826c5e658e5093f14aad1740a9b82a433e597e

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python >=3

test:
  imports:
    - importhook

about:
  home: "https://github.com/brettlangdon/importhook"
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Execute code when certain modules are imported"
  doc_url: https://brettlangdon.github.io/importhook/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tschoonj
